。 穷得只剩人参？紫鑫药业囤68亿人参还不起25亿债_上市公司股东"},"attached_info":"Cj8Itqmj3q/776lFEAMaCDcxOTMwMjI2INTjvYsGMA84kQVAL3IJNDkzNDIwMjA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5c9a4ae187eb84556a0b063c47a1ddea_720w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"48_1634796586.3832672","card_id":"Q_493416533","target":{"id":493416533,"title":"如何看待小米 MIX 4 在双十一价格大幅跳水？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/493416533","type":"question","created":1634692653,"answer_count":315,"follower_count":777,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[25405,77539,409116,725059,961372],"comment_count":50,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"首发4999起，仅2个多月，降价1000！ 相关话题：小米 MIX4 是否会变成一代跳水神机？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Itqmj3q/776lFEAMaCDcxOTI5NDA3IK3cvYsGMDI4iQZAMHIJNDkzNDE2NTMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-01636eb262fd7b61b9b8d64a55894a17_720w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1634796586.3839357","card_id":"Q_492405982","target":{"id":492405982,"title":"据说「一碗螺蛳粉的热量等于跑一场马拉松」，你还会吃螺蛳粉吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/492405982","type":"question","created":1634203933,"answer_count":252,"follower_count":454,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,974,5897,92237,379334],"comment_count":46,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Itqmj3q/776lFEAMaCDcxNzA1MDA1IJ3yn4sGMC44xgNAMXIJNDkyNDA1OTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-61209541f8e3540b3bc7a4b67996c9bb_1440w.jpg?sour